extends ../layout

block content
  section#nonprofits.section
    .container
      h2 Annual Non-Profit Support

      p.
        Each year, the Yellowstone Sea Hawkers select a local non-profit to support through
        fundraising and awareness. Since the program began, we've raised
        #[strong over $10,000] for organizations making a real difference in the Billings community.

  section.section.alt-bg
    .container
      h3 Our Supported Organizations

      .cards.cards-three
        .card
          img(src="/img/ysh_gallery4.jpg" alt="Yellowstone Valley Animal Shelter")
          .card-body
            h3 2024
            p Yellowstone Valley Animal Shelter
            p.
              We raised funds to support animal care and adoption services in the Yellowstone Valley.
            a.btn-outline(href="https://yvas.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Visit Site
            | &nbsp;
            a.btn-outline(href="https://yvas.org/make-a-gift/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Donate
        .card
          img(src="/assets/logo.png" alt="Dog Tag Buddies")
          .card-body
            h3 2025
            p Dog Tag Buddies
            p.
              Dog Tag Buddies connects veterans with service dogs, providing life-changing
              companionship and support for those who've served our country.
            a.btn-outline(href="https://www.dogtagbuddies.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Visit Site
            | &nbsp;
            a.btn-outline(href="https://tinyurl.com/DogTag-Buddies" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Donate
        .card
          img(src="/img/special-olympics.png" alt="Montana Special Olympics – Yellowstone Valley")
          .card-body
            h3 2026
            p Montana Special Olympics – Yellowstone Valley
            p.
              This season we're supporting Special Olympics Montana, which provides year-round
              sports training and competition for people with intellectual disabilities —
              including athletes right here in the Yellowstone Valley.
            a.btn-outline(href="https://somt.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Visit Site
            | &nbsp;
            a.btn-outline(href="https://support.specialolympics.org/a/montana" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Donate

  section.section
    .container
      a.btn-outline(href="/#charitable") &larr; Back to Charitable Work
